title: Vegetarian Food Xayaphom Village
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Buffet, Juice bar, Take-out, Laotian
description: Clean, no-frills eatery was started in September 2007 by a vegetarian couple with former experience in vegetarian cooking. Food is mostly vegan, with some fruit shakes made with milk and baguettes with cheese. Stir frys and soups do not contain dairy or eggs. Manager speaks English.
